OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day across the
OL,6,Fregion with early patches of low cloud
OL,7,Fand fog lifting during the morning to
OL,8,Fleave plenty of sunshine. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasantly warm in the afternoon in
OL,10,Fthe gentle mainly northerly wind.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining generally dry
OL,13,Fduring the evening and overnight.
OL,14,FThere will be clear spells, although
OL,15,Fsome low cloud is likely to reform,
OL,16,Falong with a few mist or fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
