OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAfter a locally grey and
OL,6,Fmisty start Thursday will be another
OL,7,Ffine day for many with warm sunny
OL,8,Fspells. However, there is a chance of
OL,9,Fthe odd light shower developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FIt will
OL,12,Fstay mostly fine on Friday, though
OL,13,Fmore in the way of cloud is expected.
OL,14,FOver the weekend the weather looks
OL,15,Fmore mixed with some rain developing
OL,16,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
